textbox_5.text: Colour categories, colors for me represent certain moods for instance red would be associated with blood or danger or incorrect outcome and blue or light blue would sort of represent a mild situation and finally green would describe a correct or acceptable outcome or a good mood
textbox_7.text: An amazing task however at some point while identifying the similarity between the colors of the two circles that appeared I experienced a moment where I was sort of zoned out but I think it's because I was completely trying to focus on the screen to spot the differences.
